node.text: Thanks to all who have supported this fun project! Today is the last day to preorder my first puzzle. (Link in profile) due to popular demand we did open the edition size a bit but pre-ordering is the only way to guarantee you get one. Due to the current pandemic we’ve noticed higher than normal shipping rates to some areas, we have no control over that and unfortunately we are unable to offer alternative shipping options at this time.
